Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.20,0:00:04.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在东京租界确认到巨大的爆炸
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.03,0:00:07.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,据推测是报告中提到的Freyja弹头
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.03,0:00:11.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仍滞留在神根岛是否妥当?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.81,0:00:14.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无妨 一切都交给修奈泽尔
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.89,0:00:20.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一般市民当场死亡人数逾千万
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.13,0:00:23.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事后受害者推测将达到2500万人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.58,0:00:26.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为医疗设施也被完全破坏 无法对市民进行及时救治
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.22,0:00:29.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,东京租界已死
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.67,0:00:34.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这…这种事
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.14,0:00:38.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全都…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.26,0:00:43.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全都是…我…干的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.51,0:00:46.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学园逃过一劫
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.23,0:00:50.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但这已经不是战争
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.77,0:00:55.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果再次使用这种兵器 黑骑士团将全军覆灭
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.97,0:00:58.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藤堂 是我
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.09,0:00:59.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ZERO 眼下…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.41,0:01:01.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全军降落至东京租界
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.61,0:01:02.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寻找娜娜莉
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.95,0:01:06.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下 朝比奈遇难 除此之外还有众多牺牲…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.94,0:01:08.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才不管这些
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.75,0:01:10.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到娜娜莉
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.38,0:01:11.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最优先
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.61,0:01:13.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全军动员搜寻娜娜莉
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.78,0:01:16.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个ZERO已经…

Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.00,0:02:49.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,背叛


Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.69,0:02:52.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逃亡者逃往左侧跑道
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.74,0:02:54.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下 请先重编军队
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.98,0:02:56.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道 马上回来
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.98,0:02:57.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,扇

Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.40,0:03:02.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千草


Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.55,0:03:07.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到此为止了 逃亡者
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.01,0:03:11.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,科奈莉娅?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.43,0:03:13.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原以为逃走的是维蕾塔
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.99,0:03:16.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久违了 毫无节操的电视制作人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.19,0:03:20.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是ZERO干的吗 皇女殿下成了俘虏
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.69,0:03:23.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为何不再给我多一点信任
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.09,0:03:26.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞄准腿部 活捉她
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.64,0:03:27.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.16,0:03:31.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们是布里塔尼亚的外交特使
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.92,0:03:35.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重复 我们是布里塔尼亚的外交特使
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.14,0:03:36.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无战斗意愿
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.07,0:03:38.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,外交特使?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.71,0:03:42.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水无濑 那台机体是通过正式管道申请的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.72,0:03:48.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兄长
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.63,0:03:52.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能 亲自深入敌人腹地?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.08,0:03:57.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藤堂 叫你找娜娜莉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.04,0:03:58.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亲自去指挥搜救部队
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.68,0:04:01.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡莲 听得见吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.03,0:04:02.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,罗洛 杰雷米亚
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.49,0:04:04.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,娜娜莉一定还活着 找出来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.63,0:04:06.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找出娜娜莉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.48,0:04:08.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通告全军
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.42,0:04:11.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,后退至幕张后 重整战线
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.39,0:04:13.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全军紧急撤退
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.06,0:04:15.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藤堂 我叫你找娜娜莉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.58,0:04:20.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要哥哥没事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.48,0:04:21.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,机会还会降临
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.56,0:04:24.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暂时休战是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.91,0:04:26.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,布里塔尼亚什么意思
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.41,0:04:28.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么俾斯麦要撤兵
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.43,0:04:30.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原因正在确认中
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.00,0:04:31.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但似乎没有交战意向
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.83,0:04:34.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且 东京也暂时停战了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.20,0:04:36.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是ZERO的指示吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.79,0:04:38.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,主人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.59,0:04:41.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥 振作起来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.95,0:04:43.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找娜娜莉…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.31,0:04:45.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有我在哥哥身边
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.63,0:04:48.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前不也就我们两人坚持至今
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.19,0:04:53.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杰雷米亚吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.91,0:04:55.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在想让哥哥静一下
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.15,0:04:57.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有事等一下再说
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.27,0:05:03.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗 虽然也许没太大意义
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.32,0:05:06.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥这里有我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.69,0:05:09.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你为什么会有它
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.38,0:05:13.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是原本打算给娜娜莉的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.21,0:05:14.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,娜娜莉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.55,0:05:18.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你休想代替娜娜莉 冒牌货
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.86,0:05:25.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还没察觉吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.71,0:05:27.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我痛恨你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.61,0:05:29.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,深恶痛绝
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.05,0:05:32.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,几次想害死你 不过未能如愿而已
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.92,0:05:34.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥…哥
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.42,0:05:37.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,滚出去 别再出现在我面前
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.81,0:05:39.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,滚出去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.01,0:05:47.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到头来 我仍旧没意识到 会造成怎样的损失
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.05,0:05:50.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妮娜 你必须做出选择
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.83,0:05:53.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是抛弃科学保留人心
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.38,0:05:56.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是舍弃人心来投身科学
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.28,0:05:58.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种事…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.72,0:06:01.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,罗伊德老师也遇到过这种选择吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.14,0:06:04.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我原本就道德败坏
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.90,0:06:07.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这点自知之明还是有的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.41,0:06:10.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我制造的Freyja
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.43,0:06:13.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全都是我杀的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.51,0:06:14.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全都…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.19,0:06:17.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全都
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.10,0:06:24.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 ZERO不接
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.63,0:06:26.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没办法
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.22,0:06:28.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有ZERO也得与修奈泽尔进行会谈
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.46,0:06:31.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是我们的头头是ZERO吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.02,0:06:33.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先斩后奏是不是有点不妥?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.53,0:06:38.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,屠杀 妇女儿童一个不放过 是ZERO指使的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.60,0:06:42.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迪特哈尔特 为什么没有马上抓住修奈泽尔
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.52,0:06:44.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有一架Knightmare护卫吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.49,0:06:45.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趁这机会为朝比奈报仇
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.59,0:06:48.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他的专机上装载有Freyja弹头
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.89,0:06:49.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Freyja?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.01,0:06:53.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,引发刚才巨大爆炸的元凶
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.09,0:06:57.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那里爆炸的话 我们和ZERO都难以幸免
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.23,0:07:03.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然不知修奈泽尔打的什么算盘 但现在只能由我们去会会他了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.36,0:07:05.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就免了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.11,0:07:07.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得去检修回归的红莲
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.64,0:07:11.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那交涉由我、千叶、迪特哈尔特 还有…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.51,0:07:14.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 找不到扇那家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.32,0:07:16.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底去哪了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.95,0:07:20.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡莲 你没事真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.75,0:07:22.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉让大家担心了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.25,0:07:24.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ZERO呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.83,0:07:26.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在房间
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.27,0:07:27.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,据说受伤了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.26,0:07:35.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,娜娜莉殿下 您一定要活着
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.25,0:07:36.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,活着…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.93,0:07:43.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以上就是我在教团中的所见所闻
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.66,0:07:45.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢 科奈莉娅
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.35,0:07:46.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样我…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.64,0:07:47.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.07,0:07:52.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉了 忙着照顾你们打伤的士兵
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.52,0:07:55.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玉城 刚才我也说过请自觉…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.81,0:07:59.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是黑骑士团内务清洁副官
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.45,0:08:02.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做为事务总长扇要的代理
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.40,0:08:04.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是你的一厢情愿
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.53,0:08:07.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 请务必到场
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.32,0:08:10.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玉城真一郎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.05,0:08:14.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听闻是ZERO最元老级的志同道合者 身经百战
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.85,0:08:16.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有眼光
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.29,0:08:17.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玉城
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.72,0:08:22.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,过去 我曾被你所救
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.76,0:08:25.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想来道一声谢而已
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.49,0:08:30.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 我和你之间的关系还真是奇妙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.77,0:08:33.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,命运终究让我们成为敌人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.62,0:08:36.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就此告辞
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.26,0:08:38.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我必须去找娜娜莉殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.94,0:08:45.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,娜娜莉已经…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.03,0:08:49.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幸存者排队登录
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.04,0:08:54.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姓名年龄住所血型
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.40,0:08:57.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,需要救治的人去医务接待台
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.32,0:09:02.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为避免混乱 请保持冷静
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.18,0:09:04.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,利瓦尔
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.26,0:09:07.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会长 你活着啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.20,0:09:09.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,活着 还活着
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.31,0:09:12.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.56,0:09:17.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上次和ZERO未分胜负
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.25,0:09:19.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ZERO不会来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.98,0:09:22.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必须先确认会谈内容
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.24,0:09:25.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 我想他也不会来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.21,0:09:29.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他并不是乐于与人讨论的类型
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.04,0:09:32.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,独自背负一切 与他人疏远
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.16,0:09:35.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这口吻貌似很熟悉ZERO的为人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.97,0:09:36.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比你更了解
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.59,0:09:41.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ZERO是我和科奈莉娅的弟弟
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.47,0:09:43.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.78,0:09:49.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神圣布里塔尼亚帝国前第11皇子 鲁鲁修．V．布里塔尼亚
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.36,0:09:52.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我最深爱却又敬畏的男子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.48,0:09:53.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.44,0:09:55.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ZERO是布里塔尼亚的皇子?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.17,0:09:59.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迪特哈尔特 你不可能毫无察觉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.26,0:10:03.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该从杰雷米亚和维蕾塔那里获得过情报
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.87,0:10:06.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白费心机
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.60,0:10:10.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想靠这种言论令我们自乱阵脚吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.44,0:10:15.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们认可ZERO是因为他引发的奇迹而并非家谱
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.46,0:10:19.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但这些奇迹如果有弄虚作假的话呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.16,0:10:20.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弄虚作假?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.34,0:10:23.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ZERO有特殊能力 GEASS
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.39,0:10:27.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,强制对方服从命令的能力
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.12,0:10:30.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以把它理解成一种强效的催眠术
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.27,0:10:32.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这力量是奇迹之神?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.78,0:10:35.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少说我们家ZERO的坏话
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.25,0:10:38.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他天资聪颖胆识过人 可了不起了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.71,0:10:43.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说什么皇子和GEASS 有证据吗 证据
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.96,0:10:45.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,证据在此
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.72,0:10:46.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,扇?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.79,0:10:47.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,维蕾塔也在
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.10,0:10:49.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他说得没错
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.32,0:10:53.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ZERO的真身是布里塔尼亚前皇子鲁鲁修
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.08,0:10:57.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用GEASS的力量操纵人心的 骗子



Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.00,0:11:15.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ZERO一直把我们蒙在鼓里
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.46,0:11:18.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直 把我们作为棋子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.47,0:11:20.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在说什么呢 扇
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.20,0:11:22.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但这如果当真
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.35,0:11:26.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即便如此 不能否认ZERO至今为止的功劳
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.74,0:11:31.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且如果真有GEASS的话 不是很令人鼓舞吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.09,0:11:34.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将成为对抗布里塔尼亚的强有力武器

Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.48,0:11:38.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果这份力量只对敌人使用的话
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.01,0:11:38.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.67,0:11:40.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道对我们也是?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.09,0:11:41.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.56,0:11:44.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他操纵自己的亲妹妹尤菲米娅
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.88,0:11:47.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,屠杀了前来参加日本特区的11区人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.60,0:11:48.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呆子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.57,0:11:50.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ZERO是正义的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.60,0:11:51.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种事…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.30,0:11:53.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果要证据的话就在这


Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.66,0:11:57.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鲁鲁修 你对尤菲使用了GEASS吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.62,0:11:58.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.62,0:12:00.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让她屠杀日本人?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.15,0:12:02.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我命令的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.35,0:12:05.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那次屠杀是?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.34,0:12:06.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ZERO的所作所为
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.89,0:12:08.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而非我的妹妹

Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.70,0:12:11.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ZERO下令屠杀日本人…

Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.87,0:12:13.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肯定是伪造的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.50,0:12:17.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这些是 被怀疑使用过GEASS的事件与人物
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.29,0:12:24.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,草壁 片濑少将也…

Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.56,0:12:33.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.94,0:12:35.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克洛维斯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.41,0:12:36.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也深受其害
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.92,0:12:40.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样一来高亥的替身
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.03,0:12:43.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杰雷米亚投降过来 全都得以说明

Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.83,0:12:48.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也无法保证自己有没有被他的GEASS操纵
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.31,0:12:50.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么想的话 着实可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.83,0:12:52.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道我们也…

Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.04,0:12:59.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且我们曾将Freyja弹头的事告知过ZERO
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.13,0:13:01.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为避免无谓的牺牲
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.49,0:13:04.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Lancelot上留有通信纪录
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.58,0:13:08.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 没有告诉我们


Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.13,0:13:09.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ZERO无法信任
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.31,0:13:12.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,省悟
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.47,0:13:16.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是这么的相信他….

Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.15,0:13:21.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是我们对他来说…只是棋子吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.55,0:13:24.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,畜生 ZERO这混帐
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.30,0:13:25.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,畜生
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.73,0:13:31.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位能否交出我的弟弟ZERO


Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.19,0:13:34.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有个条件
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.00,0:13:35.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,扇?

Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.79,0:13:38.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们还有讨价还价的余地吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.07,0:13:40.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愿闻其详

Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.52,0:13:43.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把日本还来

Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.90,0:13:47.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,背叛自己曾经相信的伙伴

Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.02,0:13:51.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至少要换回日本 不然我无法原谅自己

Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.51,0:14:00.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,主人 请脱下衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.37,0:14:04.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪里疼吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.17,0:14:07.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手构不着的话 我可以
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.66,0:14:14.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 无法触及之处
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.76,0:14:19.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ZERO 能进来吗 是我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.40,0:14:20.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡莲


Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.13,0:14:25.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,扇希望你去四号仓库
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.80,0:14:26.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,四号?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.25,0:14:29.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,具体情况我也不清楚


Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.22,0:14:30.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,主人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.41,0:14:34.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请脱下衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.16,0:14:36.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我试试看


Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.05,0:14:40.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在我被抓住的时候 你们都做了些什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.77,0:14:43.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是 这个C.C. …

Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.71,0:14:47.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失去了记忆

Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.40,0:14:49.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我的错

Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.22,0:14:53.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以你认识的C.C. 已经不在了

Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.95,0:15:00.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,C.C. 不在
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.33,0:15:04.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,C.C. 不在 娜娜莉也走了

Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.08,0:15:06.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那鲁鲁修呢

Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.90,0:15:09.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡莲 你没事就好

Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.76,0:15:11.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉营救来晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.89,0:15:16.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鲁鲁修 我和娜娜莉谈了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.01,0:15:18.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是她帮了我

Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.07,0:15:24.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种时候说也许不合适 我的哥哥…

Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.10,0:15:30.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,觉悟吧 ZERO

Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.40,0:15:33.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟将我们玩弄于鼓掌中
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.08,0:15:35.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们已经知道你的GEASS

Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.98,0:15:42.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,传说的英雄ZERO 壮志未成身先死
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.21,0:15:47.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但他勇敢的生前事迹 将被人们永久传颂

Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.19,0:15:50.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迪特哈尔特 这就是你的剧本吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.26,0:15:55.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原本打算拍完你战胜布里塔尼亚的一幕
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.55,0:15:58.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很遗憾 节目被腰斩了

Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.90,0:16:02.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么办 虽然Knightmare碍事 但扇他们毫无防备
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.78,0:16:04.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偷偷使用GEASS的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.65,0:16:06.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都那么相信你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.82,0:16:09.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,井上和吉田也是为你而死

Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.78,0:16:12.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 这样太单方面了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.50,0:16:15.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多亏ZERO我们才走到今天不是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.50,0:16:16.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也听他一言

Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.37,0:16:17.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让开 卡莲

Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.80,0:16:19.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想和ZERO陪葬吗


Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.38,0:16:21.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不会中了GEASS吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.93,0:16:26.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回答我 鲁鲁修
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.73,0:16:29.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对你来说 我是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.10,0:16:32.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我愿意和你…


Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.80,0:16:39.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来是你干的…


Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.26,0:16:43.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那看来没机会了…

Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.71,0:16:45.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托你 回答我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.03,0:16:50.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傻瓜 事到如今才察觉吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.65,0:16:54.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自己被利用了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.40,0:16:57.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们不过是棋子而已


Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.80,0:16:59.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ZERO 你果然…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.51,0:17:00.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ZERO

Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.27,0:17:02.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鲁鲁修

Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.70,0:17:04.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡莲


Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.72,0:17:07.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是一颗特别优秀的棋子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.82,0:17:10.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错 这不过是一盘棋
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.78,0:17:12.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一场游戏
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.23,0:17:14.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗


Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.40,0:17:19.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,永别了 鲁鲁修
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.80,0:17:21.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,举枪


Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.00,0:17:25.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡莲 你要活下去

Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.30,0:17:27.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开枪

Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.60,0:17:31.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系 哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.90,0:17:32.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,罗洛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.50,0:17:34.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无所谓 连蜃气楼一起解决

Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.30,0:17:35.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.98,0:17:37.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥由我保护
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.40,0:17:42.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别这样 罗洛

Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.66,0:17:43.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经够了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.29,0:17:46.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,主人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.19,0:17:49.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,消失了 蜃气楼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.59,0:17:51.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和巴别塔那时一样

Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.60,0:17:53.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿妮亚 ZERO逃了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.59,0:17:55.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Mordred能抓住吗

Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.76,0:17:58.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,摧毁的话
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.05,0:18:08.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝对守护领域的计算没想到这么辛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.58,0:18:12.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的哥哥果然厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.07,0:18:14.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,罗洛 我已经没有活下去的理由
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.71,0:18:22.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么 这动作
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.78,0:18:25.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝不会让你死
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.76,0:18:28.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么大范围使用GEASS
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.75,0:18:32.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,罗洛 这样下去你的心脏承受不了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.27,0:18:35.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通告全员 蜃气楼被偷走
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.68,0:18:38.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所有战斗单位全力摧毁蜃气楼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.09,0:18:40.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重复 摧毁蜃气楼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.59,0:18:48.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,够了 罗洛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.05,0:18:49.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已经…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.04,0:18:50.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.42,0:18:51.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.48,0:18:52.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.89,0:19:03.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直被人作为道具
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.94,0:19:05.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…住手 罗洛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.32,0:19:06.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么要…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.58,0:19:09.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是教团的道具
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.46,0:19:13.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…救我 我…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.92,0:19:16.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之后又被哥哥…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.76,0:19:21.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的确也许只是被哥哥利用
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.22,0:19:26.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 那段时光是真实的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.71,0:19:29.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对你…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.86,0:19:31.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为那段回忆
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.60,0:19:36.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我终于可以 成为人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.89,0:19:39.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别这样
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.30,0:19:40.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,罗洛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.70,0:19:44.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 已经…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.37,0:19:46.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.99,0:19:50.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手 别使用GEASS
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.25,0:19:51.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想死吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.37,0:19:55.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我 不是道具
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.96,0:20:00.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是我的意志

Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.40,0:20:14.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,罗洛 为什么救我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.96,0:20:16.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我对你…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.04,0:20:20.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥是个骗子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.77,0:20:26.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这也是谎话吧 说什么想杀我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.48,0:20:29.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说什么恨我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.55,0:20:30.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.05,0:20:32.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞒不过你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.84,0:20:35.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是我的弟弟

Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.23,0:20:38.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.61,0:20:43.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我对哥哥…最了解…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.05,0:20:48.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 是的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.88,0:20:52.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的哥哥是个骗子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.73,0:20:56.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无法确认目标
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.11,0:20:57.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,扩大搜索范围
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.80,0:20:59.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请增派地面班
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.22,0:21:12.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,娜娜莉 罗洛 夏莉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.78,0:21:14.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑骑士团
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.34,0:21:16.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我失去了一切
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.72,0:21:18.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是结局
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.98,0:21:20.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 报应才对
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.64,0:21:26.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 正因为如此 谢谢 罗洛
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.50,0:21:32.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你救回的这条性命 对我来说还有必须做完的事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.81,0:21:35.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 对我来说
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.19,0:21:42.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没想到 会被迫使用这里的系统
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.40,0:21:45.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诸神的黄昏的接续
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.80,0:21:51.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,旧的世界会被毁灭 新的世界将会被创造
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.39,0:21:55.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吾父 查尔斯．D．布里塔尼亚啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.86,0:22:00.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去地狱的路上 少不了你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.53,0:22:01.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是…

Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.76,0:23:42.06,Default,,0,0,0,,那么 我和你到底是什么关系呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.85,0:23:45.99,Default,,0,0,0,,还真是奇怪呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.69,0:23:49.24,Default,,0,0,0,,我已经知晓了真相  我…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.68,0:23:53.59,Default,,0,0,0,,追随我到最后的 竟然是你
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.41,0:23:57.82,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 我总是后知后觉呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.67,0:24:01.79,Default,,0,0,0,,你不是鲁路修·Vi·布里塔尼亚的
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.04,0:24:04.08,Default,,0,0,0,,而是鲁路修·兰佩路基的弟弟
